headline: C.H. Robinson delivers on AI, but investors still skeptical
summary: Despite processing over 3 million tasks with generative AI, C.H. Robinson’s stock continues to face pressure amid a sluggish freight market and investor caution. The post C.H. Robinson delivers on AI, but investors still skeptical appeared first on FreightWaves.
